===Intransitive verb===
'''to fry'''
#To [[cook]] in hot [[fat]].
#(''colloquial'') To suffer because of too much heat.
#:''You'll fry if you go out in this sun with no sunblock on.''
#(''colloquial'') To be [[execute]]d by the [[electric chair]].
#:''He's guilty of murder - he's going to fry.''

